{"tid":2119440,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下邊個聯賽唔係一兩隊強隊獨大？？","createTime":"2020-07-22T06:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T17:02:42.000Z","uid":43785,"like":38,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"c997b21fb1599ef77c0d86676ce438d5c184055b","tid":2119440,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:01:11.000Z","msg":"有D聯賽球迷成日睇到自己喜歡果個聯賽好勁，好高人一等，其實有冇諗過五大聯賽都係海軍鬥水兵相差真係唔多，都係強隊玩晒。<br />\n<br />\n英超，唔好同我講乜野BIG幾，利記曼城爭左幾年，大拋其他隊，近幾年來來去去都係呢兩隊玩<br />\n<br />\n西甲，基本上俾人叫巴甲，年年都巴塞贏，皇馬間唔中有一次，馬體會連基沙文都走埋就行撚開啦。根本只有兩隊獨大。<br />\n<br />\n德甲，拜仁，比盡你咪計埋多蒙特，其實都冇得爭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意甲，祖記，今年國米拉素前期緊咬，武肺後跌晒。<br />\n<br />\n法甲，巴黎成日提早登基<br />\n<br />\n其實冇邊個聯賽可以懶清高話自己多競爭。<br />\n年年都係呢一兩隊攞。<br />\n成日笑我西甲同德法意甲獨大，你英超咪一柒樣。"},{"pid":"99b23de22d009f10eefb83e27ceaf073524dcfdf","tid":2119440,"uid":72405,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:01:33.000Z","msg":"你點問的"},{"pid":"ae828163bde58e45757757a0b11d69c804005bc2","tid":2119440,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:01:36.000Z","msg":"Sir"},{"pid":"c247ea1c5b583672a611fc9aa45fb5074d52d71c","tid":2119440,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99b23de22d009f10eefb83e27ceaf073524dcfdf","tid":2119440,"uid":72405,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:01:33.000Z","msg":"你點問的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:01:49.000Z","msg":"慢左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb356706bffa33d0272c60060cd2a7ec20ef0de7","tid":2119440,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:01:51.000Z","msg":"你點想的"},{"pid":"22fb290a6d9caf1ba1d015e83a23c89c8a8a67f4","tid":2119440,"uid":141668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:01:57.000Z","msg":"你點獨的"},{"pid":"b10b8d713a80c059993f3275c790c1c8a9eb73ad","tid":2119440,"uid":143499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020