文都走埋就行撚開啦。根本只有兩隊獨大。<br />\n<br />\n德甲，拜仁，比盡你咪計埋多蒙特，其實都冇得爭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意甲，祖記，今年國米拉素前期緊咬，武肺後跌晒。<br />\n<br />\n法甲，巴黎成日提早登基<br />\n<br />\n其實冇邊個聯賽可以懶清高話自己多競爭。<br />\n年年都係呢一兩隊攞。<br />\n成日笑我西甲同德法意甲獨大，你英超咪一柒樣。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:05:04.000Z","msg":"利記曼城都係爭左2年姐...."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:14:43.000Z","msg":"唔爭咪曼城囉，一樣獨大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:14:02.000Z","msg":"車路士呢"},{"pid":"ee8f5c56429c9098a5829e358ee8e495789d08ce","tid":2119440,"uid":209773,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"cb0a68cce3275af13c9432b9e03a42d7c562be3e","tid":2119440,"uid":72962,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"921b01ad133f958cf1bbe068c97f0a2eebaa58ea","tid":2119440,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"280ca5d52f65ecd2b904b7572d6da937959d084c","tid":2119440,"uid":226816,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:17:34.000Z","msg":"兩年前先曼聯拎第二 之前熱刺又排過第二<br />\n<br />\n又點樣曼城利記爭左幾年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:26:12.000Z","msg":"祖後面，咪又係年年洗牌。<br />\n<br />\n皇巴後面，咪又係跟英超情況一柒樣，沒有誰比誰高尚。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:49:55.000Z","msg":"三年前干地先拎完<br />\n又點呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:14:28.000Z","msg":"樓主弱能"},{"pid":"2a1c91bdfe97ae480f7929b3d3674665ae85c362","tid":2119440,"uid":17722,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ef25dbb10b790aa67ba3a0fa7168ddb7ac412feb","tid":2119440,"uid":204243,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NtWU1Uf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtWU1Uf.jpg&h=4dab865d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n樓主唔好勞氣, 用事實數據去論證"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:19:13.000Z","msg":"根本英超唔係一兩隊獨大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c1e7d7600affc2bd7b100b42293b060927947a","tid":2119440,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7ab7fcc500d99b4a57ac16c